metadata.description: The Welly Santa Claus Edition is the first in a series of collectible NFTs released by the Welly team. These NFTs are designed to bring good vibes and holiday cheer, and are being released as a way for the Welly team to interact with their community. The Welly Santa Claus Edition NFTs have only artistic value and some 1/1 were distributed to the luckiest members of the community from the main Welly NFT collection.
metadata.name: Welly Santa Claus Edition
